Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text:
The Perimeter — home to Atlanta’s largest office submarket — has been, and continues to be, one of Atlanta’s fastest-growing regions. Located just inside the I-285 loop, Perimeter Summit offers easy access to intown Atlanta with what the locals call “OTP” (outside the perimeter) conveniences.

GDOT’s Transform 285/400 highway infrastructure project will bring interchange improvements to Perimeter Summit, decreasing commute times and simplifying access from I-285 / GA-400. The project entered its final phase in February, 2020 and is slated to be completed in 2021.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Perimeter Summit offers premier Class A office in an inspiring park-like campus with on-site dining, conferencing and event facilities, state-of-the-art fitness, a 4-star, 4-diamond Hyatt Regency hotel, walking trails, lightning-fast wi-fi, and more.
